while loading data if using docker
copy csv to docker
steps :
1. docker ps ( it will give details and container name) 
2. docker cp "file path" continername:/var/opt/mssql/data/

after successfully copying data to docker conatiner then load 


--load bulk data --

truncate table bronze.crm_cust_info ;
bulk insert bronze.crm_cust_info 
from '/var/opt/mssql/data/cust_info.csv'
with(
    firstrow=2,
    fieldterminator=',',
    tablock
);

